OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774973462
OL,3,CRoy Hodgson says he's 'not just here
OL,4,Cfor a ride' as he returns to Bristol
OL,5,CCity
OL,7,FFormer England manager Roy Hodgson has
OL,8,Fsaid he's "not just here for a ride"
OL,9,Fafter being appointed interim manager
OL,10,Fof Bristol City until the end of the
OL,11,Fseason.
OL,13,FAt 78, Hodgson returns to Ashton Gate
OL,14,F44 years after the club sacked him
OL,15,Ffollowing just four months in charge.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
