PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774973462
OL,3,CRoy Hodgson says he's 'not just here
OL,4,Cfor a ride' as he returns to Bristol
OL,5,CCity
OL,7,FIn one of the more astonishing
OL,8,Fappointments not only of this but any
OL,9,Fseason, the former England boss has
OL,10,Fcome out of retirement to fill a
OL,11,Fvacancy left by the dismissal of
OL,12,FGerhard Struber last week following a
OL,13,Fpoor run of results.
OL,15,FHodgson's renaissance is only expected
OL,16,Fto last for the seven remaining games
OL,17,Fof City's season, but he told a packed
OL,18,Fnews conference on Monday he was
OL,19,Frelishing the opportunity to get back
OL,20,Finto a sport he's been around for half
OL,21,Fa century.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774973462
OL,3,CRoy Hodgson says he's 'not just here
OL,4,Cfor a ride' as he returns to Bristol
OL,5,CCity
OL,7,FHodgson said: "I've been perfectly
OL,8,Fhappy in retirement, a little bit
OL,9,Fbored from time to time, but a
OL,10,Fchallenge like this was hard to turn
OL,11,Fdown.
OL,13,F"I hope to get some enjoyment from
OL,14,Fbeing here, to reenergise myself a
OL,15,Flittle bit by being back on the grass
OL,16,Fand being back with players, something
OL,17,Fwhich has always been what I wanted to
OL,18,Fdo."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774973462
OL,3,CRoy Hodgson says he's 'not just here
OL,4,Cfor a ride' as he returns to Bristol
OL,5,CCity
OL,7,FHe added: "I'm not just here for a
OL,8,Fride. I'm hoping that with my
OL,9,Fexperience and the way I work, some of
OL,10,Fthat might be different, and if it's
OL,11,Fany good, I'm hoping that will be of
OL,12,Fvalue."
OL,14,FThis is Hodgson's 24th managerial
OL,15,Fappointment, making him the oldest
OL,16,Fmanager in English football.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774973462
OL,3,CRoy Hodgson says he's 'not just here
OL,4,Cfor a ride' as he returns to Bristol
OL,5,CCity
OL,7,FHis last job in management ended when
OL,8,Fhe left Crystal Palace in February
OL,9,F2024, with many, probably including
OL,10,Fthe man himself, thinking he would
OL,11,Ffinally enjoy an overdue retirement.
OL,13,FBut new Bristol City Chief Executive
OL,14,FCharlie Boss explained that when the
OL,15,Fclub became aware of Hodgson's
OL,16,Finterest in the role, it was keen to
OL,17,Fsign him.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774973462
OL,3,CRoy Hodgson says he's 'not just here
OL,4,Cfor a ride' as he returns to Bristol
OL,5,CCity
OL,7,FBoss said: "I definitely wouldn't have
OL,8,Fmade a change unless I was really
OL,9,Fconfident that we had a plan to make
OL,10,Fthe most of these last 7 games.
OL,12,F"We talked about who could not only
OL,13,Fbring quality coaching over the
OL,14,Fremaining 7 games, but who could also
OL,15,Fbring something that would last longer
OL,16,Fthan that, and the name at the top of
OL,17,Four list was Roy's, so I couldn't be
OL,18,Fmore delighted that that has
OL,19,Fmaterialised."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774973462
OL,3,CRoy Hodgson says he's 'not just here
OL,4,Cfor a ride' as he returns to Bristol
OL,5,CCity
OL,7,F"I really see this as something that
OL,8,Fhas an impact that can hopefully lead
OL,9,Fon from beyond this season into future
OL,10,Fyears," Boss added.
OL,12,FHodgson's managerial career began with
OL,13,FSwedish side Halmstad in 1976. He was
OL,14,Ffirst appointed at City in 1982 when
OL,15,Fthe club was blighted by a financial
OL,16,Fcrisis which almost saw them lose
OL,17,Ftheir Football League status.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774973462
OL,3,CRoy Hodgson says he's 'not just here
OL,4,Cfor a ride' as he returns to Bristol
OL,5,CCity
OL,7,FDespite the short-lived tenure, he
OL,8,Fwent on to take some of the biggest
OL,9,Froles in football, not least an
OL,10,Fultimately ill-fated reign as England
OL,11,Fboss from 2012-16.
OL,13,FHe's also managed the national sides
OL,14,Ffor Switzerland, Finland and the
OL,15,FUnited Arab Emirates, but it was in
OL,16,Fclub football that he enjoyed perhaps
OL,17,Fhis greatest success, both at home and
OL,18,Fabroad, with Inter Milan, Fulham and
OL,19,FWest Bromwich Albion.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774973462
OL,3,CRoy Hodgson says he's 'not just here
OL,4,Cfor a ride' as he returns to Bristol
OL,5,CCity
OL,7,FBristol City is in the process of
OL,8,Fappointing a sporting director before
OL,9,Fbringing in a new, permanent head
OL,10,Fcoach in a bid to reverse the side's
OL,11,Ffortunes.
OL,13,FThe Robins started the season well
OL,14,Fwith ambitions of a second successive
OL,15,Fplay-off appearance, but now sit 16th
OL,16,Fin the Championship table.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774973462
OL,3,CRoy Hodgson says he's 'not just here
OL,4,Cfor a ride' as he returns to Bristol
OL,5,CCity
OL,7,FA perceived lack of investment from
OL,8,Fthe board following the sale of
OL,9,Fseveral star names has led to growing
OL,10,Fanger amongst fans who will be hoping
OL,11,Fthat Hodgson's appointment can at
OL,12,Fleast end their campaign on a high.
OL,14,FBoss said: "I absolutely understand
OL,15,Fthe frustration that fans feel, but
OL,16,Fthis decision really has to be about
OL,17,Flooking forward rather than looking
OL,18,Fback.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774973462
OL,3,CRoy Hodgson says he's 'not just here
OL,4,Cfor a ride' as he returns to Bristol
OL,5,CCity
OL,7,F"What I feel really confident in is
OL,8,Fthat fans recognise the need for us to
OL,9,Fchange if we're going to attain that
OL,10,FPremier League status we're striving
OL,11,Ffor, and this is part of that change."
OL,13,FHodgson's first game in charge will be
OL,14,Fthe Championship trip to Charlton on
OL,15,FGood Friday.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
